OL,3,C'We can't afford anything': Inside
OL,4,CGlastonbury's growing van dweller
OL,5,Ccommunity
OL,7,FVan dwellers in a Somerset town say
OL,8,Fthey have "no other choice" but to
OL,9,Flive on wheels as the cost of living
OL,10,Fcrisis intensifies.
OL,12,FIn Glastonbury, there are
OL,13,Fapproximately 300 people who call
OL,14,Ftheir van or caravan home.
OL,16,FIt is thought the ratio of caravans to
OL,17,Fregular homes is one of the highest -
OL,18,Fif not the highest - in the country.
