OL,4,CGlastonbury's growing van dweller
OL,5,Ccommunity
OL,7,FSomerset Council wants to build a
OL,8,Fregulated site but there are fears
OL,9,Fthis may only encourage more roadside
OL,10,Fparking because of associated costs.
OL,12,F'A nationwide crisis' - van dweller
OL,14,FJess told ITV News West Country: "It's
OL,15,Fnot a council issue, it's a nationwide
OL,16,Fcrisis of housing affordability.
OL,18,F"Van living is becoming more popular
OL,19,Fbecause people simply can't afford
OL,20,Fefficient housing anymore."
