OL,7,FLuke added: "Policy needs to change.
OL,8,FThere are so many people under 35 who
OL,9,Fcan't afford houses or land - we can't
OL,10,Fafford anything at the moment."
OL,12,FCompared to the number of regular
OL,13,Fhomes in Glastonbury, the proportion
OL,14,Fof van dwellers is higher than
OL,15,FBristol, a city with five approved
OL,16,Fsites for van dwellers.
OL,18,FLived-in vehicles are bumper-to-bumper
OL,19,Fin certain areas of Bristol, like
OL,20,FClifton Downs.
