OL,8,Ftheir number has quadrupled over the
OL,9,Fpast five years to more than 600.
OL,11,FFor six decades, Glastonbury has
OL,12,Fattracted those seeking alternative
OL,13,Flifestyles - though the large influx
OL,14,Fof van dwellers has caused some
OL,15,Fchallenges for residents.
OL,17,FLocal gym owner Adam said: "I've had
OL,18,Fpeople turn up with axes and knives,
OL,19,Fdemanding I turn the music down.
