OL,5,Ccommunity
OL,7,F"I'm simply running a business in a
OL,8,Fnon-residential area, and they've
OL,9,Fdecided to park their caravans right
OL,10,Foutside, even dumping rubbish near my
OL,11,Fgym."
OL,13,FThe issue is being considered by
OL,14,FSomerset Council as they weigh-up
OL,15,Foptions for regulated off-road sites
OL,16,Fand affordable housing.
OL,18,FLiberal Democrat Councillor Liz
OL,19,FLeyshon said: "It's going to be
OL,20,Fextremely challenging to provide
OL,21,Fenough off-road sites.
